[[Callisto]] is a level 470 bear that can be found inside [[Callisto's Den]]. He is killed for the valuable [[voidwaker hilt]], [[claws of callisto]], [[tyrannical ring]], and [[Callisto cub]], though he can also drop the [[dragon 2h sword]] and [[dragon pickaxe]]. Completion of the medium [[Wilderness Diary]] is required to fight Callisto.

'''{{Colour|red|Warning}}:''' Like all [[Wilderness bosses]], Callisto resides in a [[multi-way]] area and in level 39  [[Wilderness]]. You may be attacked at any time during the kill. '''Do not''' bring any items that you are not willing to lose.

